I" <h3 id="the-basics">The Basics</h3>

<hr />

<ul>
  <li>Loading happens when we don’t have any data. But we’re fetching the data.</li>
  <li>Fetching happens when we have some data already. And we’re fetching data.</li>
</ul>

<p>It’s a good UX practice to differentiate Loading and Fetching.</p>

<h3 id="loading-vs-fetching">Loading vs Fetching</h3>

<hr />

